@NODE "playing" "How to play"
@TOC "MAIN"
                              Playing the game
                             ------------------
  Simple. Just point to the number you wish to move to the blank space
  (marked by a white asterisk (*)) and click the mouse. If it is a 
  legal move (you are allowed to move the numbers wich are raised), the
  selected tile and the blank space will switch places. Do this until all 
  numbers are in order (1-15 and the blank at the end). When this is 
  accomplished you have won the game!
  
  Both the number of moves that have been made and the time taken will
  be calculated but I haven't made a highscore function yet. This means
  that your best scores won't be saved (if it's important to you there's
  always pen and paper).
  
@ENDNODE

